JOB OFFERS

   Remintrex – Multichannel ReTargeting developed an innovative online
   marketing service that helps companies to significantly improve their
   conversion rate. Our service works for e-mail and phone retargeting
   campaigns and it is performance-based, thus there are no fixed costs.

   It can be conveniently used for campaign managements and controlling
   and CRM. Our clients include classic e-commerce providers, portals and
   agencies.

   At the moment, we are strengthening our team in Berlin and we are
   looking for:

     * Sales Manager (Full-time)

   Apply now

